description:
- Create a table to store aggregated instance statistics (counts).
- Expose the records via GraphQL

DB structure:

* `id` (pkey)
* `object`, integer(2) / enum
* `recorded_at`, datetime
* `count`, integer(8)
* no timestamp columns

Proposed GraphQL API:

```
instanceStatistics(last: 1) {
  mergeRequests {
    count
    recordedAt
  }
  users {
    count
    recordedAt
  }
  groups {
    count
    recordedAt
  }
  ...more objects
}
```
